---
title: Mussels in a Aromatic Broth with Crispy Herbed Fries and Toasted Ciabatta
description: Quick and simple, a meal of 'Moules Frites' is French food at its best! Enjoy tender mussels and the classic flavour combination of shallots and garlic with crisp and golden, herb-tossed fries. Garlic mayo makes a bold and creamy dip for potatoes. Soak up the fragrant broth with toasted ciabatta.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/mussels-in-a-aromatic-broth-8d1afa64.jpg
